txt.en: 'Hi there! Are you ready to get caught up with the story? I can complete the next two chapters of the Black Book of Mordor for you, as well as the Interlude: Shades in the Swamp.\n\n'Speak to me when you're ready, and I'll put pen to paper and write this all down!'
Completion of this quest will flag your character as having completed the Black Book of Mordor, Chapters 9 and 10, as well as Interlude: Shades in the Swamp.
Talk to MadeOfLions to complete chapters 9 and 10 of the Black Book of Mordor and the Interlude.
'Ready to complete chapters 9 and 10 of the Black Book of Mordor, and the Interlude: Shades in the Swamp? Here we go!'
